# WorldEdit - Minestom Platform (MinestomWorldEdit)

![Minestom Extension](https://img.shields.io/badge/Minestom-Extension-important?style=for-the-badge&logo=data:image/png;base64,)

This repo contains an unofficial implementation of a WorldEdit platform for the [Minestom](https://github.com/Minestom/Minestom) server implementation.
